cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper deals with facial expression recognition in videos using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method involves attention mechanisms, which are also used in multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the application of facial expression recognition has implications in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) research.
